latestPosts.caption: When your bridal lehenga wasn’t just another piece of clothing you owned. 🤍

Two sketches. Two stories. Both unforgettable.

The Baroque Heart – Designed in a custom plum, this lehenga carries intricate hearts, crafted to hold quiet vows and whispered promises.

The Jasmine – Drenched in shifting greens and blues, this lehenga is a moving tribute to nature, light, fluid, and full of life.

Which one’s speaking to you?

latestPosts.caption: A vision of modern romance Meera Sakhrani (@meerasakhrani ) weaves magic in our AVELYN lehenga set, creating a bridal look as soft and ethereal as a feather.

She twirled once…
And in that quiet spin, her mother saw it,

Not just a lehenga.
But the moment her little girl became a bride.

The Alice Lehenga. Chosen with love.

✔️Mobility is the key, test your leg movement, ensure ease around the knees for graceful movement, to walk comfortably, climb stairs & dance. 
✔️Do lift up the fish cut lehenga during trial so you don’t end up doing the restroom tango! 
Restroom breaks should be manageable, choose soft can-can over stiff ones for easier handling and practicality. 
Can you manage a restroom break without removing the fishcut change?
✔️ Add extra flair at the bottom, it will allow you to opt for hidden sneakers/platform heels for comfort that doesn’t compromise style. 

Because beauty should never come at the cost of comfort 🤍
